Geocache Description:

This cache has been plundered of all of its contents, but the bucket still remains.

near Salem, OR. (Divine Stash = exactly at degrees)

Yep, the Worlds First Divine Stash is now in place at N45 0.000 W123 0.000
using WSG84. Divine comes from a contraction of 'dividing line'.

The stash contains Money, Gold, Jewelry, MRE, Soy Sauce, Alphatone, and of
course a Log Book for you to log your visit, but I forgot to put in a pen to
write with...

The rules are: Take Something,,,, Leave Something... or at least write
something.

There is an old iron witness post marking the spot, there is a benchmark some
distance away on the freeway overpass.

I hope the witness post keeps the freeway grass mowing machines from trashing
the stash..

Have Fun finding it !!

Dave...

(Note: Original description restored from The Internet Archive and the sci.geo.satellite-nav newsgroup. -Admin)
